<http://www.example.org/emdco> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/creator> "Harmanjeet Singh Kaur"@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> "This ontology models the EUDAMED catalogue including devices, manufacturers, identified risks, incidents and field safety corrective actions (FSCA)."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title> "European Medical Device Catalogue Ontology (EMDCO)"@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontology for the European catalogue of high-risk medical devices under MDR (EU 2017/745) and IVDR (EU 2017/746)."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "European Medical Device Catalogue Ontology"@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "1.0.0" .
