<http://www.example.org/emdco#addressesIncident> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Incident> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#addressesIncident> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a field safety corrective action to the incident that triggered it."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#addressesIncident> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "addresses incident"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#affectsDeviceType
<http://www.example.org/emdco#affectsDeviceType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
