<http://www.example.org/emdco#associatedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Risk> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#associatedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates an incident to the identified risk category according to IMDRF nomenclature."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#associatedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "associated risk"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#hasManufacturer
<http://www.example.org/emdco#hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
