<http://www.example.org/emdco#hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a device to its regulatory risk classification."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has risk class"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#involvedDevice
<http://www.example.org/emdco#involvedDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
