<http://www.example.org/emdco#isSubclassifiedUnder> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/emdco#RiskClass> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isSubclassifiedUnder> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Transitive property relating a risk class to a higher-level risk class in the MDR/IVDR classification hierarchy."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isSubclassifiedUnder> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is subclassified under"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#issuedBy
<http://www.example.org/emdco#issuedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
