<http://www.example.org/emdco#issuedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a field safety corrective action to the manufacturer who issued it."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#issuedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "issued by"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#reportedBy
<http://www.example.org/emdco#reportedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#reportedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Incident> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#reportedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Manufacturer> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#reportedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates an incident to the manufacturer who submitted the report to EUDAMED."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#reportedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "reported by"@en .
