<http://www.example.org/emdco#incidentID> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#incidentID> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Incident> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#incidentID> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#incidentID> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Unique identifier for the incident in EUDAMED."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#incidentID> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "incident ID"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#intendedPurpose
<http://www.example.org/emdco#intendedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#intendedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Device> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#intendedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#intendedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The intended use of the device as declared by the manufacturer."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#intendedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "intended purpose"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#isActive
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isActive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Device> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates whether the device operation depends on an external energy source."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is active"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#isIVD
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isIVD> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isIVD> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Device> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isIVD> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isIVD> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates whether the device is an in vitro diagnostic device regulated under IVDR."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isIVD> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is IVD"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#isImplantable
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isImplantable> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isImplantable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Device> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isImplantable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isImplantable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates whether the device is intended to be implanted in the human body."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isImplantable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is implantable"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/emdco#Device> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates whether the device can be reused after appropriate reprocessing."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is reusable"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#manufacturerID
<http://www.example.org/emdco#manufacturerID> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
