<http://www.example.org/emdco#manufacturerID> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The unique manufacturer identifier in EUDAMED."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#manufacturerID> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "manufacturer ID"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#manufacturerName
<http://www.example.org/emdco#manufacturerName> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
