<http://www.example.org/emdco#status> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#status> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The current status of the corrective action: Open or Closed."@en .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#status> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "status"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/emdco#udiDI
